Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE "MOJON ELEMENTARY SCHOOL," IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF MALOLOS, PROVINCE OF BULACAN, TO THAT OF "BARASOAIN MEMORIAL ELEMENTARY SCHOOL."
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 336, June 19, 1938 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE "MOJON ELEMENTARY SCHOOL," IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF MALOLOS, PROVINCE OF BULACAN, TO THAT OF "BARASOAIN MEMORIAL ELEMENTARY SCHOOL."
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of the "Mojon Elementary School," in the municipality of Malolos, Province of Bulacan, is hereby changed to that of "Barasoain Memorial Elementary School."
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.(aw√ûhi(
Enacted, without Executive approval, June 19, 1938.
